race.comment: CHIEF OF STAFF (1) is first-up here but was well in the betting prior to the spell and where there's smoke there's fire. Plenty of scratchings help and can run a big race while fresh. STEIN (12) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown a bit at the trials and any push in betting should be noted. LILSISTERDON'TCHA (11) showed enough on debut before being sent for a spell to mature. That was enough to warrant consideration in a race like this. DOMINANT DARCY (8) draws the inside marble and cannot be left out of calculations. HELLO CAPTAIN (5) gets Thompson on board and is next in line from the low draw.
